rows.label: tlk00340103_msg0001
rows.name:
Us Mercs, we respect hard work
and dedication, so we can't afford
to skimp on our training.

rows.label: tlk00340103_msg0002
rows.name:
You guys are traveling with the Holy Grail,
so it's especially important to keep
yourselves in good shape.

rows.label: tlk00340103_msg0003
rows.name:
You can't afford to rely on others to
help you out in a pinch. You gotta
learn to protect yourselves.
